                                    LEVEL 1

(IF YOU GET KILLED, PRESS 'CTRL-C' WHILE IT PLAYS THE MUSIC AND YOU WON'T DIE)
E, E, GET KETTLE, N, KILL SKELETON, GET KEY, S, S, KILL BEETLE, S, KNOCK DOOR,
GO DOOR, W, KILL BERSERKER, GET LODESTONE, E, N, E, S, S, KILL MUMMY, S, GET
SCROLL, S, KILL BUGBEAR, GET BOTTLE, W, UNLOCK DOOR, GO DOOR, S, KILL KOBOLD,
W, W, GET MIRROR, N, KILL GNOLL, GET WOLVESBANE, S, E, E, S, S, E, S, S, KILL
TOAD, GET EYES, N, N, W, N, N, N, W, N, N, N, E, E, S, GO STAIRWAY


                                    LEVEL 2

S, KILL GOBLIN, GET OIL, S, E, N, KILL ZOMBIE, N, GET BOOK, N, KILL ORC, GET
VIAL, W, N, W, KILL GNOME, GET POUCH, OPEN POUCH, GET MADWEED, E, S, E, E, USE
LODESTONE, GO DOOR, W, N, KILL DRAGON, GET BLOOD, S, E, S, W, S, S, S, S, KILL
SLIME, DROP KEY, GET BELLADONNA, S, E, OPEN DOOR, GO DOOR, E, N, KILL SPIDER,
N, N, KILL NEWT, DROP POUCH, CHOP TONGUE, GET TONGUE, S, OPEN DOOR, GO DOOR, E,
S, S, KILL RAT, DROP LODESTONE, CHOP TAIL, GET TAIL, E, S, U, OPEN VIAL, GET
ACONITE, MIX INGREDIENTS, DRINK POTION, READ SCROLL, SAY ALDORAGAMBA, LOOK
MIRROR.

